NAME
        tomcat-ctl - Control tomcat from the command line with simplicity

SYNOPSIS
        > tomcat-ctl install -v 5.5.35
        > tomcat-ctl list
        > tomcat-ctl up -v 5.5.35
        > tomcat-ctl down
        > tomcat-ctl restart
        > tomcat-ctl ping

REQUIREMENTS
  General
        perl 5.10 or greater
        HTTP::Tiny

  Windows
        7za (the command line version of 7zip) installed in C:\Users\[USERNAME]\bin
        for install command

  Unix
        GNU tar (on PATH) for install command

AUTHOR
        Delon Newman <delon.newman@gmail.com>

